{"tid":474931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人靜落黎個陣 會變得好負面？","createTime":"2017-11-20T15:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T00:06:36.000Z","uid":13910,"like":198,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"8059319ba10251205cf48195226dd95fc8222d7f","tid":474931,"uid":13910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲同我一樣<br />\n當你放工/放學 自己一個搭車個陣 望住出面d風景+聽歌<br />\n就會諗好多野 學業 家庭 愛情 咩都諗一餐 但諗既係負面野 然後想喊下 但係公眾地方 又唔敢喊 屈住屈住咁 好辛苦 然後 原來咁又一日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：21歲 學生"},{"pid":"91099e851fe576e6cda04ac3884817dd1e11b109","tid":474931,"uid":140604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴絲同我一樣<br />\n當你放工/放學 自己一個搭車個陣 望住出面d風景+聽歌<br />\n就會諗好多野 學業 家庭 愛情 咩都諗一餐 但諗既係負面野 然後想喊下 但係公眾地方 又唔敢喊 屈住屈住咁 好辛苦 然後 原來咁又一日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：21歲 學生</blockquote><br />\n呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  you are not alone"},{"pid":"49f29e6d382a6fed2ed665f0bafcc367e33e688e","tid":474931,"uid":22505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"d眼淚根本就按制唔到流出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b92d3b203735a0cfa0617707542a48d8fe6a7b","tid":474931,"uid":117911,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:55:19.000Z","msg":"成日都喺咁，好似已經慣左，人地一兩句都夠你諗一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767250dd08437fd64e02b9f0daf7343582cd182c","tid":474931,"uid":71524,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"係架<br />\n有時放工放學返到屋企沖沖下涼就喊<br />\n又返學又返工真係好攰好辛苦<br />\n有時真係問自己我究竟做緊乜野？呢個係唔係生活黎？<br />\n點解好似冇曬自己咁"},{"pid":"64ada6ebfec288f57efd4359686fef734fe19899","tid":474931,"uid":13910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"我日日都係咁 點算好<br />\n有時見到人會諗<br />\n點解佢可以咁開心 笑笑口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4a347560bfc728692ad63577ba88493290cb1f","tid":474931,"uid":117911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我日日都係咁 點算好<br />\n有時見到人會諗<br />\n點解佢可以咁開心 笑笑口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要一齊陪笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 幾多人都好，你個樣笑得幾開心都好，你跟本就覺得好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf25a5ff414cc93c45d5b71304560a887311f8f","tid":474931,"uid":101455,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"本身對住朋友都好開心<br />\n不過靜落黎自己一個果時都會諗好多野<br />\n未來，學業，事業同愛情，<br />\n好多野都好似好唔完滿，<br />\n自己點努力都差緊啲。<br />\n<br />\n覺得生存真係好攰，<br />\n但我唔會死只係呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68024dd50c469a7dfc63dcebca0a1a44896c888","tid":474931,"uid":106539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"以為自己開緊post 近期更加嚴重左"},{"pid":"ebb714e6ece0756b43e31553774a5bc0ebf5ee79","tid":474931,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:39:03.000Z","msg":"深夜放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好凍好頹好唔開心"},{"pid":"8f6d3aafc1984b87c0dc8620317d7bbbb8033e17","tid":474931,"uid":13910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深夜放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好凍好頹好唔開心</blockquote><br />\n你唔係凍 同樣 我都唔係凍<br />\n只係空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febea4bbdcc487b7c7969139d24468c0dacad6b2","tid":474931,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n聽下d歌，治療一下，好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c97442e04e58a225cf0485bdc2a33aad0bf9ec","tid":474931,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>深夜放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好凍好頹好唔開心</blockquote><br />\n你唔係凍 同樣 我都唔係凍<br />\n只係空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 心靈都幾空虛 冇野想做 冇野令我著迷"},{"pid":"8055c4678057b78ef71cfd4c39af1d1f41e1d3fe","tid":474931,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"香港人先會咁"},{"pid":"6174e76f404a9278c36c11e019a0918a7f8125af","tid":474931,"uid":14935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:53:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/Ycw1314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYcw1314&d=y%2BRqw0hR3gSMVi7XQM28Di7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=8b1f2756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Ycw1314</a><br />\n巴打可以搵我傾下計 我都咁岩想搵人開解下"},{"pid":"a6cd4a8e5dd6667e1f83372816a3ee7c159cbd1a","tid":474931,"uid":51165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:56:53.000Z","msg":"一個人嘅時候成日都好杞人憂天，乜都諗一餐 煩一餐 驚一餐，所有嘢都好容易諗到最壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁係咪有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35070c02c2f0fffce64fa34526390249fa1df719","tid":474931,"uid":68258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T17:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3f97ff15bab929f2fc9a4aaee38d96895d4b81","tid":474931,"uid":13910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T17:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人嘅時候成日都好杞人憂天，乜都諗一餐 煩一餐 驚一餐，所有嘢都好容易諗到最壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor